## Target scope (authoritative boundary)

Paste **one** concrete scope per run. The agent MUST treat it as the hard boundary unless [Scope expansion rules](#scope-expansion-rules) apply.

### Scope template

```txt
TARGET_SCOPE:
lib/features/<module>/<area>/**
app/(main)/[locale]/o/[orgSlug]/apps/<module>/<segment>/**
tests/unit/<matching>*.test.ts
tests/e2e/<matching>*.spec.ts
