| --- | --- | --- |
| `lib/features/hrm/<area>/...` | `lib/features/hrm/<area>/**` + matching `app/.../apps/hrm/<segment>/**` + `tests/**/hrm*` | `hrm` |
| `lib/features/contacts/...` | `lib/features/contacts/**` + `app/.../apps/contacts/**` + `tests/**/contacts*` | `contacts` |
| `lib/features/org-admin/...` | `lib/features/org-admin/**` + `app/.../admin/**` + `tests/**/org-admin*` | `org-admin` |
