## Gold references by pattern

Pick the closest on-disk reference **before coding**. Do not invent a new pattern family when one already exists.

| Pattern | When | Reference |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **A** | Page chrome + bespoke forms | `#features/governed-surface` — `GovernedSurface`, `ModulePageHeader`, `GovernedSection` |
| **B** | Lists/KPI/stats without trailing row forms | `lib/features/contacts/components/contacts-page.tsx` |
| **C** | List + trailing forms/actions | `lib/features/hrm/employee-management/employee-lifecycle-management/components/hrm-onboarding-section.tsx` |
| **K (footer-actions)** | Kanban with footer actions | `lib/features/hrm/talent-management/recruitment-onboarding/components/recruitment-pipeline-kanban-section.tsx` |
| **K (drag / claims)** | Kanban drag or claims pipeline | `lib/features/hrm/payroll-compensation/expenses-reimbursement/components/claim-kanban-section.tsx` |
| **Thin app route** | ERP page wiring only | `app/(main)/[locale]/o/[orgSlug]/apps/contacts/page.tsx` |
| **Org admin** | Admin workbench surface | `lib/features/org-admin/` + matching `app/.../admin/` page |
| **Portal** | External/constrained audience | `components2/portal-shell/` + `lib/portal/` guards |

**Pattern selection verdict:**

```txt
MUST match existing UI shape — do not swap Pattern B for C (or vice versa) if output changes.
MUST use GovernedComponentRenderer / GovernedPatternCListSection / Kanban sections only when ADR-0026 + gold reference support that shape.
MUST NOT deep-import renderer internals when a public door exists.
```

