## Execution workflow

Complete the job **end-to-end in one pass**.

```txt
1. Read authoritative inputs + required skills for TARGET_SCOPE / REFACTOR_KIND
2. Audit current implementation (internal — output only if blocked)
3. Make smallest safe change set that satisfies verdicts while preserving UI
4. Update actions, queries, schemas, metadata, exports, routes, tests together when same contract
