## Status vocabulary (strict)

For every requirement, use **exactly one**:

| Status | Meaning |
| --- | --- |
| `prepared` | Structure/contracts ready; runtime/engine/integration not fully implemented |
| `partial` | Some runtime behavior exists; gaps remain |
| `complete` | Runtime behavior implemented **and** verified |
| `blocked` | Concrete blocker outside task control — evidence required |

